  }, "v15"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA n\u1ED5i gi\u1EADn c\xF9ng A-ma-xia cho n\xEAn Ng\xE0i sai m\u1ED9t nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri \u0111\u1EBFn n\xF3i v\u1EDBi vua r\u1EB1ng, \"T\u1EA1i sao vua nh\u1EDD c\xE1c th\u1EA7n kh\xE1c gi\xFAp m\xECnh? Ch\xFAng n\xF3 c\xF2n kh\xF4ng \u0111\u1EE7 s\u1EE9c c\u1EE9u d\xE2n ch\xFAng n\xF3 kh\u1ECFi tay vua n\u1EEFa l\xE0!\" "), mdx("h6", {
