  }, "v16"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110ang khi nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri \u0111ang n\xF3i th\xEC A-ma-xia b\u1EA3o, \"Ai giao cho anh nhi\u1EC7m v\u1EE5 c\u1ED1 v\u1EA5n cho vua? C\xE2m mi\u1EC7ng \u0111i n\u1EBFu kh\xF4ng l\xE0 m\u1EA5t m\u1EA1ng \u0111\xF3.\" Nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri li\u1EC1n im ti\u1EBFng nh\u01B0ng n\xF3i th\xEAm, \"T\xF4i bi\u1EBFt Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF nh\u1EA5t \u0111\u1ECBnh ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t vua v\xEC vua \u0111\xE3 l\xE0m \u0111i\u1EC1u n\u1EA7y. Vua kh\xF4ng th\xE8m nghe l\u1EDDi khuy\xEAn c\u1EE7a t\xF4i.\" "), mdx("h6", {
